The swamp was home to both [[werecrocodile]]s and [[wererat]]s, which were in frequent conflict with each other.

The native [[werecrocodile]]s had a half-sunken [[City of the Werecrocodiles|city]] on the seaward edge of the swamp{{Cite polyhedron/108/Forgotten Deities: Sebek|4}} By the late 15{{th}} century [[DR]], the werecrocodiles' domain had expanded throughout the swamp as the nation of [[Sebakar (nation)|Sebakar]].

The chaotic [[halfling]] barony of [[Ursuma]] was founded within the swamp sometime before [[1372 DR]].<ref>{{Cite web/Halflings in Chessenta: The Bard of Adder Swamp}}
